// Deel AI Chat injection

;(async function () {
  let disableDeelAIChat = true;

  const localeParam = window.location.pathname.split('/')[1];
  const locales = ["en", "fr", "de", "es", "pt", "ja", "nl", "ko-kr", "zh-cn", "zh-tw", "sv-se", "da-dk"]
  const isLocale = locales.includes(localeParam);
  const disabledPaths = ['/careers', '/plp', '/paid-lp', '/events'];

   for (const path of disabledPaths) {
    if (window.location.pathname.startsWith(!isLocale ? path : '/' + localeParam + path)) {
      console.log('Deel AI Chat is disabled for path');
      return;
    }
  }

  const maxHour = 16;
  const minHour = 5;
  const getUserCountry = async () => {
    const country = await fetch('https://get.geojs.io/v1/ip/country.json')
      .then((res) => res.json())
      .then((data) => data.country)
    return country
  }

  const getUserTimezone = () => {
    return Intl.DateTimeFormat().resolvedOptions().timeZone
  }

  const isUserFromNA = (country = '') => {
    return ['US', 'CA', 'MX', 'USA', 'CAN', 'MEX'].includes(country)
  }

  const isUserBetween5amAnd5pm = (timezone = '') => {
    const now = new Date()  
    const nowInTimezone = new Date(now.toLocaleString('en-US', { timeZone: timezone }))
    const hour = nowInTimezone.getHours()
    return hour >= minHour && hour <= maxHour;
  }

  const isWeekdayInNAM = (timeZone) => {
    const date = new Date(
      new Date().toLocaleString("en-US", { timeZone })
    );

    const day = date.getDay(); // 0 = Sun, 6 = Sat
    return day >= 1 && day <= 5;
  }

  const getTimeoutUntilHour = (targetHour, timeZone) => {
    const now = new Date();

    // Local time fallback
    if (!timeZone) {
      const target = new Date(now);
      target.setHours(targetHour, 0, 0, 0);
      return Math.max(0, target - now);
    }

    // Get current date/time parts in the target timezone
    const parts = new Intl.DateTimeFormat('en-US', {
      timeZone,
      year: 'numeric',
      month: '2-digit',
      day: '2-digit',
      hour: '2-digit',
      minute: '2-digit',
      second: '2-digit',
      hour12: false
    }).formatToParts(now);

    const get = t => Number(parts.find(p => p.type === t).value);

    const year = get('year');
    const month = get('month') - 1;
    const day = get('day');
    const hour = get('hour');
    const minute = get('minute');
    const second = get('second');

    // Already past target hour
    if (hour >= targetHour) return 0;

    // "Now" in target timezone as UTC ms
    const nowInTZ = Date.UTC(year, month, day, hour, minute, second);

    // Target time in target timezone as UTC ms
    const targetInTZ = Date.UTC(year, month, day, targetHour, 0, 0);

    return Math.max(0, targetInTZ - nowInTZ);
  };

  const setChatCookie = (value) => {
    const date = new Date(new Date().setTime(new Date().getTime() + 315360000000))
    const expires = '; expires=' + date.toUTCString()
    document.cookie = 'deel_ai_chat' + '=' + value + expires + '; path=/'
  }

  const enableNA_AIChat = async () => {
    const timezone = getUserTimezone()
    const isBetween5amAnd5pm = isUserBetween5amAnd5pm(timezone)
    const isWeekday = isWeekdayInNAM(timezone)
    
    if (!isBetween5amAnd5pm || !isWeekday) {
      // clear cookie
      document.cookie = 'deel_ai_chat' + '=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/'
    }
      
    const cookie = document.cookie.match('(^| )\s*deel_ai_chat\s*=\s*([^;]+)')?.[2] || ''
    if (cookie === 'true') {
      return false
    }

    const country = await getUserCountry()
    const isFromNA = isUserFromNA(country)

    return isFromNA && isBetween5amAnd5pm && isWeekday
  }

  const isNA_AIChatEnabled = await enableNA_AIChat();

  const enableChatParam =
    new URLSearchParams(window.location.search).get('enable_deel_ai_chat') === 'true'

  if (enableChatParam || isNA_AIChatEnabled) {
      setChatCookie('true');
  }

  const cookie = document.cookie.match('(^| )\s*deel_ai_chat\s*=\s*([^;]+)')?.[2] || ''
  disableDeelAIChat = cookie === 'true' ? false : true

  if (disableDeelAIChat) {
    console.log('Deel AI Chat is disabled via flag')
    return;
  }

  const timezone = getUserTimezone();
  const timeoutUntil = getTimeoutUntilHour(17, timezone);
  const isWeekday = isWeekdayInNAM(timezone)
  
  // Disable AI Chat on weekends
  if (!isWeekday) {
    console.log('Deel AI Chat is disabled via timezone on weekends');
              
    // Clear the cookie
    document.cookie = 'deel_ai_chat' + '=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/';

    return;
  }

  const timeoutCountdown = timeoutUntil < 3000 ? 3000 : timeoutUntil;

  setTimeout(() => {
    // Hide the widget element
    const chatElement = document.querySelector('.deelAIChat_container');
    if (chatElement) {
        chatElement.style.display = 'none';
    }
    
    // set disableDeelAIChat to true
    disableDeelAIChat = true;
      
    // Also try to hide via the API if available
    if (window.deelAIChat) {
        window.deelAIChat?.styleSheet && (window.deelAIChat.styleSheet.disabled = true);
        window.deelAIChat?.setView && window.deelAIChat.setView(null);
    }
          
    // Clear the cookie
    document.cookie = 'deel_ai_chat' + '=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/';
          
    console.log('Deel AI Chat hidden at 5pm');
  }, timeoutCountdown);

  console.log('AI Chat script loaded, pathname:', window.location.pathname)
  console.log('Full URL:', window.location.href)

  // Prevent multiple initializations
   if (window.deelAIChatInitialized) {
    return;
  }

  window.deelAIChatInitialized = true;

  function isInIframe() {
    try {
      return window.self !== window.top;
    } catch (e) {
      return true;
    }
  }
  
  function initDeelAIChat() {
    console.log('initDeelAIChat called');
    
    if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {   
      // If we're in an iframe, inject the script into the parent window
      if (isInIframe()) {
        console.log('In iframe, sending message to parent to initialize AI chat');
        window.parent.postMessage(['initDeelAIChat'], '*');
        return;
      }
      
      // If we're in the parent window, initialize the chat
      const disableDeelAIChat = false;
      function dataLayerEvent(message_contents) {
        const { eventAction, eventProduct, ...rest } = message_contents;
        if (window.dataLayer) {
          window.dataLayer.push({
            event: 'interaction',
            event_product: eventProduct || 'Deel AI Chat',
            event_action: eventAction,
            ...(rest ? rest : {}),
          });
        }
      }
      
      // Wait for document.body to be available
      function waitForBody(callback) {
        if (document.body) {
          callback();
        } else {
          setTimeout(() => waitForBody(callback), 100);
        }
      }
      
      waitForBody(function() {
        // Check if script is already loaded
        if (document.getElementById('deel_chat') || window.deelAIChat) {
          return;
        }
        
        (function (d, s, id, cb) {
          if(disableDeelAIChat){
            return;
          }

          var js = d.createElement(s);
          var n = d.createElement('div');
          n.id = id;
          if (js.readyState) {
            js.onreadystatechange = function () {
              if (js.readyState === 'loaded' || js.readyState === 'complete') {
                js.onreadystatechange = null;
                cb();
              }
            };
          } else {
            js.onload = function () {
              cb();
            };
          }
          js.src = "https://growth-tools.deel.com/scripts/deel-ai-chat-v2.js";
          document.body.appendChild(js);
          document.body.appendChild(n);
      })(document, 'script', 'deel_chat', function () {
        if(typeof window === 'undefined' || window.location.pathname.includes("/request-a-demo")){
          return;
        }
        const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        const updatedQueryString = urlParams.toString();
        const updatedUrl = window.location.pathname + (updatedQueryString ? '?' + updatedQueryString : '');
        window.history.replaceState({}, '', updatedUrl);

        if (window.deelAIChat) {
          console.log('initializing deelAIChat');
          window.deelAIChat.init({
            deelAIChatUrl: "https://growth-tools.deel.com/deel-ai-chat",

            redirectUri: window.location.origin + window.location.pathname,
            messageHistoryPersistHours: 1,
            aiMode: 'faster',
            upfrontQuestions: [
              'I want to book a demo call',
              'How can Deel help my business grow?',
            ],
            onError: function (error) {
              console.error('Error occurred', error);
            },
            onEvent: function (payload) {
              dataLayerEvent(payload);
            },
          });
          console.log('deelAIChat.init() called successfully');
        } else {
          console.error('deelAIChat not available');
        }
      });
      });
    }
  }
  
  // Listen for messages from iframe to initialize AI chat in parent
  window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
    if (Array.isArray(event.data) && event.data[0] === 'initDeelAIChat') {
      console.log('Received initDeelAIChat message from iframe');
      initDeelAIChat();
    }
  });
  
  // Try to initialize immediately
  initDeelAIChat();
  
  // Also try when DOM is ready
  if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initDeelAIChat);

  // And when window is fully loaded
  window.addEventListener('load', initDeelAIChat);
